      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Botanischer Garten zu Hamburg ¶ Esteemed President, ¶ Nees von Esenbeck was Presidentof theAcademia Caesarea Leopoldino-Carolina Naturae Curiosorum (theLeopoldina). ¶ Among the youn ¶ ger botanists, D...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">M57.04.27</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Johannes Lehmann<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Christian<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Nees von Esenbeck</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Archiv, Deutsche Akademie der Naturforscher Leopoldina, Halle.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="formtext" style="color: #2F5496; ">Botanischer Garten zu Hamburg</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Verehrter Herr Präsident,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Unter den jüngern<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Botanikern<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>hat sich der Dr Ferdinand Müller zu Melbourne, ein geborner Holsteiner, in den letzten Jahren vortheilhaft ausgezeichnet, wie Sie aus den interessanten<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Berichten über seine Reisen und Entdeckungen in Neu-Holland in Hookers Journal of Botany werden ersehen haben. Ich selbst besitze von Müllers Schriften nur<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>den beifolgende<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>[Serie], aber auch<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>diese und Hookers Berichte denke ich werden genügen um meine Bitte zu unterstützen den Dr Müller unter die Mitglieder unserer Academie aufnehmen und mir das Diplom zur Weiterbeförderung zu kommen lassen zu wollen. Für Müller möchte ich den Namen Labillardière oder Lechenault vorschlagen, und wenn diese<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>schon<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>vergeben sein sollten, den Namen eines anderen<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Reisenden, welcher in der dortigen Gegend gesammelt hat.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>[…]</seg>
               <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.1666in; text-indent: -0.1666in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The remainder of the letter includes a nomination of Dr Ludwig Pappe of Hamburg and comments on a paper by Dr J. Milde in<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Botanische Zeitung</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">, vol.</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>15 (1857).</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ihr</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">treu ergebenster</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Lehmann</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Hamburg den 27tn April</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>1857.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Botanischer Garten zu Hamburg</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Esteemed President,</seg>
               <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.1666in; text-indent: -0.1666in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Nees von Esenbeck was President<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">of the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Academia Caesarea Leopoldino-Carolina Naturae Curiosorum (the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Leopoldina</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">)</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Among the youn</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">ger botanists, Dr Ferdinand Mueller</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>of Melbourne, born in Holstein,</seg>
               <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.1666in; text-indent: -0.1666in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M was in fact born in Rostock, Mecklenberg. He moved with his family to Tönning, in<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Schleswig-</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Holstein, when he was 10 years old, following the death of his father.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>has distinguished himself<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">to advantage<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">in the last few years, as you will have seen from the interesting reports in<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Hooker</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">'</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">s Journal</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>of Botany</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>on his journeys</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and discoveries in New Holland. Of Mueller</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">'</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">s writings</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">,</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I have only the enclosed<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">series</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>myself, but even these and Hooker</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">'</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">s reports will I think<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">be sufficient to support my request to admit Dr Mueller among the members of our Academy and to send me the diploma for transmission. I would like to su</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">ggest the names Labillardière or</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Lechenault</seg>
               <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.1666in; text-indent: -0.1666in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>i.e. Leschenault. When M was elected, however, on 1 May 1857, the cognomen assigned to him followed Lehmann's spelling<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(see Academia Caesarea Leopoldino-Carolina Naturae Curiosorum to M, 1 May 1857).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>for Mueller and if<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">these<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">should</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>already<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">be<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">assigned, the name of another traveller, who has collected in the region there.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>[…]</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Your truly devoted</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Lehmann</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Hamburg, 27 April 1857.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
   </text>
